  "title": "Introduction to Music Theory",
  "lessonText": "Music theory is the foundation of understanding and creating music.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Music theory helps you understand the structure of music.\n- It includes concepts like notes, scales, chords, and rhythm.\n- Knowing music theory enhances your playing and composing skills.\n- It provides a common language for musicians."
  }
